{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Choose a legal structure for a new business"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/legal-structures-new-business.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/legal-structures-new-business"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"B693","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"","overview":"The types of legal business structure you can choose when you're starting a new business","updated_at":"2012-10-08T12:28:46+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must choose a business structure when you start a new business.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>The structure you choose will define your legal responsibilities, like:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the paperwork you must fill in to get started</li>\n  <li>the taxes you&rsquo;ll have to manage and pay</li>\n  <li>how you can personally take the profit your business makes</li>\n  <li>your personal responsibilities if your business makes a loss</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Most businesses in the UK are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/set-up-sole-trader\" title=\"Set up as a sole trader\">sole traders</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/limited-company-formation\" title=\"Setting up a limited company\">limited companies</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/set-up-business-partnership\" title=\"Set up a business partnership\">partnerships</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"Setting up","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/business%2Fsetting-up.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes self assessment, self-employment and starting a business","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.c